        {
            "id": 6011027,
            "title": "勤誠5月營收年增逾4成寫同期高 Q2受惠AI需求帶動展望正向",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>伺服器機殼廠勤誠 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8210:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8210\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8210-TW</a>) 今 (6) 日公告 5 月營收 18.33 億元，受到匯率波動影響，月減約 7%，不過年增超過 4 成，仍創歷史同期新高。勤誠指出，受惠終端客戶的 AI 及通用型伺服器需求暢旺，第二季展望正向。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011027%2Fl%2Fb775630bf8e16109abee0809f92e76d6.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">勤誠5月營收年增逾4成寫同期高，Q2受惠AI需求帶動展望正向。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>勤誠 5 月營收 18.33 億元，月減 7.17%，年增 46.92%，寫下歷史同期新高；累計今年前 5 月營收 79.62 億元，年增 57.5%，同樣創歷史同期新高。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>展望下半年，勤誠表示，目前觀察終端客戶的 AI 及通用型機種專案需求暢旺，但美國關稅政策仍具不確定性，將持續觀察關稅後續發展，並積極與客戶進行策略討論，並加速在地化製造的布局。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>針對全球布局，勤誠美國加州 NCT 廠預計第三季開始試產，馬來西亞廠則預計在 6 月動工，規劃作為量產使用。同時，勤誠也正在評估美國德州、歐洲及印度廠，未來 3 至 5 年可能有設廠規劃。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>另外，勤誠持續深化與 CSP 與 SI 合作，推進多元機種整合方案，今年開始也成功切入客製化機櫃，目前專案進展順利，預期下半年起逐步貢獻營收，並挹注成長動能。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
