            "id": 6010992,
            "title": "臺灣50指數成分股新增台光電、刪除欣興 6/20盤後生效",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>臺灣指數公司今 (6) 日代富時羅素公布臺灣 50 指數、臺灣中型 100 指數、臺灣資訊科技指數、臺灣發達指數及臺灣高股息指數定期審核結果。其中，臺灣 50 指數新增納入台光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2383-TW</a>)、刪除欣興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>)。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010992%2Fl%2F56c885de0be30206d6a2a8fbd49cae93.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">臺灣50指數成分股新增台光電、刪除欣興 6/20盤後生效。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>而投資人最關注的臺灣高股息指數，此次成分股大幅調整，納入凱基金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2883:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2883\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2883-TW</a>)、寶成 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:9904:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/9904\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">9904-TW</a>)、信邦 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3023:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3023\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3023-TW</a>)、台新金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2887:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2887\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2887-TW</a>)、統一 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1216:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1216\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1216-TW</a>) 5 檔；同時刪除台光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2383-TW</a>)、興富發 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2542:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2542\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2542-TW</a>)、材料 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4763:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4763\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4763-TW</a>)、南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>)、陽明 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2609:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2609\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2609-TW</a>)。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>臺灣中型 100 指數成分股納入大成 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1210:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1210\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1210-TW</a>)、亞翔 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6139:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6139\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6139-TW</a>)、欣興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>)；同時刪除台光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2383-TW</a>)、台玻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1802:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1802\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1802-TW</a>)、裕隆 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2201:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2201\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2201-TW</a>)。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>臺灣發達指數成分股納入大成 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1210:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1210\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1210-TW</a>)、亞翔 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6139:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6139\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6139-TW</a>)；同時刪除台玻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1802:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1802\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1802-TW</a>)、裕隆 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2201:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2201\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2201-TW</a>)。而臺灣資訊科技指數此次成分股並無調整。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>相關成分股納入及刪除之變動將自 2025 年 6 月 20 日交易結束後生效 (亦即自 6 月 23 日起生效)。如有指數成分股在下次定期審核前之期間被刪除，將以本次候補名單遞補，候補名單自即日起生效。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>此外，臺灣高股息指數自指數審核生效日起之連續五個交易日為指數定期審核過渡期，此期間每檔股票之權重採用過渡期間權重，過渡期間生效日為 2025 年 6 月 23 日、24 日、25 日、26 日和 27 日。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
